version_description:
This release will include the following:
· Minor bug fixes
· Implement messaging for users who may be subject to certain employer stock trade restrictions
· Improve the login experience and implement the latest security standards. The first time you access your account after the changes go into effect, you’ll be prompted to change your password and setup text or email for profile recovery.

What do you think of the Voya Retire app? If you like us, please leave a review in the App store.
Problems or suggestions for improvements? Please email us at VoyaRetire@voya.com

This release will include the following:
· Updated login experience. Implemented the latest security standards to keep your account information secure. The first time you access your account after the changes go into effect, you may be prompted to change your password and setup text or email codes for device recognition and recovery of login information as needed.
· Minor bug fixes
· Balance information is now available for your non-Qualified account (if applicable to your plan)

What do you think of the Voya Retire app? If you like us, please leave a review in the App store.
Problems or suggestions for improvements? Please email us at VoyaRetire@voya.com
